```plantuml
@startuml onlybakam_reinvent2022-vote-app

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AWS AppSync (GraphQL)" as AppSync
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "SNS" as SNS
participant "AWS Translate" as Translate

User -> Frontend: Selects team (BR/CM) and message
Frontend -> AppSync: AddVote mutation
activate AppSync

AppSync -> DynamoDB: Save vote data
activate DynamoDB
DynamoDB --> AppSync: Vote saved
deactivate DynamoDB

AppSync -> SNS: Publish vote event
activate SNS
SNS --> AppSync: Event published
deactivate SNS

AppSync -> Translate: Translate message
activate Translate
Translate --> AppSync: Translated message
deactivate Translate

AppSync --> Frontend: Vote confirmation
deactivate AppSync

Frontend -> AppSync: Subscribe to OnPlusOne
activate AppSync
AppSync -> Frontend: Real-time vote updates
deactivate AppSync

@enduml
```